	(25, 39, '', '1', '', 'Nicky Raxworth', '', 'File review - Nicky Raxworth by Anshul Aggarwal', '2021-07-28 08:52:10', '2021-07-28 08:52:32', 7, 0, '{"info":{"client":"Nicky Raxworth","adviser":"39","policyType":["1"],"providers":[""],"policyNumber":"","replacement":"","showstep_1":"true","showstep_2":"true","showstep_3":"true","showstep_4":"true","showstep_5":"true","showstep_6":"true","training_needed_1":"true","training_needed_2":"true","training_needed_3":"true","training_needed_4":"true","training_needed_5":"true","training_needed_6":"true","filename":"File review - Nicky Raxworth by Anshul Aggarwal"},"step1":[{"value":"","question":"Can you evidence you meet all applicable Disclosure Regulations?","notes":""},{"value":"","question":"Can you evidence that you clearly explain the extent (scope) of services and products you can provide and <span class=\\"font-weight-bold\\">areas of competency<\\/span> including any limitations to your authorities, potential or know conflicts of interest so a client can make an informed choice whether to use your services?","notes":""},{"value":"","question":"Can you evidence where and how you explain <span class=\\"font-weight-bold\\">your<\\/span> role and obligations of care and skill etc as well as discuss <span class=\\"font-weight-bold\\">their<\\/span> obligations \\/responsibilities? e.g.\\n\\nYour process and how you will put their interests first and comply with the Code\\nTheir obligation re provision of information and consequences of not doing so.","notes":""},{"value":"","question":"Can you evidence that the <span class=\\"font-weight-bold\\">Nature and Scope of Advice<\\/span> for the <span class=\\"font-weight-bold\\">Engagement<\\/span> (including any limitations) discussed, agreed and documented before proceeding with the advice process?","notes":""},{"value":"","question":"Can you evidence that your remuneration for service has been explained and agreed?","notes":""},{"value":"","question":"If a client declines