ct features and options comparisons (loss or gain)<\\/li><li>Existence of special concessions in existing cover<\\/li><li>Impact of new health conditions, occupation, pursuits and habits on any proposed cover (potential loss of benefits \\/cover)<\\/li><li>Premium projections and comparisons over the longer term<\\/li><\\/ul>                                            ","notes":"<font color=\\"green\\">Omar Khay Margen<\\/font> - 27 August 2021 - 01:14 PM<br>testing note from the compliance officer.","with_bgcolor":"yes"},{"value":"2","question":"\\n                                                &lt;input type=\\"text\\" name=\\"with_bgcolor\\" value=\\"\\"&gt;\\n                                                <span class=\\"font-weight-bold\\">Do you consider and model different solution options<\\/span> based on client needs, client needs, circumstances and\\/or client priorities.                                            ","notes":"","with_bgcolor":""},{"value":"2","question":"\\n                                                &lt;input type=\\"text\\" name=\\"with_bgcolor\\" value=\\"\\"&gt;\\n                                                Do you carry out relevant research and analysis to identify products and providers which provide solutions to meet the client\\u2019s needs and circumstances. This may have included (but not limited to) such things as:<ul><li>Availability of product structures, options and benefits that match required strategies (including <span class=\\"font-weight-bold\\">ownership options<\\/span> and premium structures)<\\/li><li>Premium comparisons over the short and longer term<\\/li><li>Provider financial standing<\\/li><li>Possible underwriting outcomes by different providers<\\/li><li>Provider reputation and adviser experiences<\\/li><\\/ul>                                            ","notes":"","with_bgcolor":""},{"value":"2","question":"\\n                                                &lt;input type=\\"text\\" name=\\"with_bgcolor\\" value=\\"\\"&gt;\\n                                                Do you identify and evaluate any <span class=\\"font-weight-bold\\">reasonably foreseeable limitations, risks and disadvantages<\\/span> of the products or solutions recommended.                                            ","notes":"","with_bgcolor":""},{"value":"2","question":"\\n                                                &lt;input type=\\"text\\" name=\\"with_bgcolor\\" value=\\"\\"&gt;\\n                                                Are notes on your <span class=\\"font-weight-bold\\">rationale<\\/span> leading to the advice (research and analysis outcomes as above) documented and on file?                                            ","notes":"<font color=\\"green\\">Omar Khay Margen<\\/font> - 27 August 2021 - 01:14 PM<br>testing note from the compliance officer.","with_bgcolor":"yes"},{"value":"2","question":"\\n                                                &lt;input type=\\"text\\" name=\\"with_bgcolor\\" value=\\"\\"&gt;\\n                                                Are you satisfied any <span class=\\"font-weight-bold\\">product research<\\/span> or analysis not conducted by you can be relied upon and can you demonstrate this?                                            ","notes":"","with_bgcolor":""},{"value":"2","question":"\\n                                                &lt;input type=\\"text\\" name=\\"with_bgcolor\\" value=\\"\\"&gt;\\n                                                Do you identify and evaluate areas where the client needs to get <span class=\\"font-weight-bold\\">specialist advice<\\/span> such as a legal, estate planning or accounting                                            ","notes":"<font color=\\"green\\">Omar Khay Margen<\\/font> - 27 August 2021 - 01:14 PM<br>testing note from the compliance officer.","with_bgcolor":"yes"}],"step4":[{"value":"2","question":"\\n                                                &lt;input type=\\"text\\" name=\