                           &lt;input type=\\"text\\" name=\\"with_bgcolor\\" value=\\"\\"&gt;\\n                                                Do you summarise <span class=\\"font-weight-bold\\">key relevant <u>facts<\\/u><\\/span> and <span class=\\"font-weight-bold\\">client circumstances<\\/span> on which your advice is based?                                            ","notes":"<font color=\\"green\\">Omar Khay Margen<\\/font> - 27 August 2021 - 01:15 PM<br>testing note from the compliance officer.","with_bgcolor":"yes"},{"value":"2","question":"\\n                                                &lt;input type=\\"text\\" name=\\"with_bgcolor\\" value=\\"\\"&gt;\\n                                                Do you summarise the client\\u2019s core <span class=\\"font-weight-bold\\">needs and objectives<\\/span> (in personal and practical terms) and their priorities?                                            ","notes":"<font color=\\"green\\">Omar Khay Margen<\\/font> - 27 August 2021 - 01:15 PM<br>testing note from the compliance officer.","with_bgcolor":"yes"},{"value":"2","question":"\\n                                                &lt;input type=\\"text\\" name=\\"with_bgcolor\\" value=\\"\\"&gt;\\n                                                Does the advice clearly outline any considerations in arriving at your advice? For example:<ul><li>Client\\u2019s risks tolerance\\/capacity<\\/li><li>Priorities<\\/li><li>Choice of product provider<\\/li><li>Known limitations to the advice e.g. needs identified but unable to address, insufficient information provided<\\/li><li>Reasons for cancelling or retaining existing cover<\\/li><li>Any restrictions to being able to provide best possible solution e.g. health status of client and any alternative risk management strategies<\\/li><li>Government support available and their impact<\\/li><li>Tax implications<\\/li><\\/ul>                                            ","notes":"","with_bgcolor":""},{"value":"2","q